        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 11.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、星見プロダクションです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ this is Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "やあ、僕だよ\n僕",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. It’s me.\nme.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……まさか井川葵か！？　びっくりした\nオレオレ詐欺みたいな言い方はよしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Aoi Igawa?! What a surprise.\nDon't make it sound like a scam.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.833333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、兄さん\n今から言う口座にすぐ500円振り込んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Listen up‚ buddy.\nWire 500 yen to my account or you’re in big trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ……\n冗談はいいから用件を言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jeez…\nEnough kidding around. What do you want?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "今日ライブがあるんだけど控え室に来てくれない？\n時間は八時くらいかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have a live today. Could you come backstage?\nIt starts around 8. Something like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "君に見せたいものがあるんだ\nじゃあ後で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve got something to show you.\nSee you then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1113.3333332999982,
          "startTime": 44.48
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、待ってくれ、俺にも都合が――\nって切れてる……全く、本当にマイペースな子だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hold on! I do have a life of my own――\nShe hung up. She sure does things on her own terms.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8299.999999999996,
          "startTime": 56
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 55.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 55.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ彼女達のステージを観るのは勉強になるけど……\n特に葵のダンスは完璧で、非の打ち所がなかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this was a good opportunity to see them perform.\nAoi‚ especially‚ I’d give her a perfect score. Her dancing was flawless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "僕的にはまだ七十五点くらいなんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d rate it a 75 out of 100 at best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "来てくれたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You came.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お、お疲れ様。今日はありがとう\nいいもの見せてもらったよ。差し入れ、どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "G-great job. Thanks for today.\nYou put on a great performance. Here’s a little something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、君は律儀な人だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? What a polite person you are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ケーキとピンクの花束か\n可愛いのは僕には似合わないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But a cake and pink flowers?\nCute doesn’t suit me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないと思うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wouldn’t say that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな？　まあいいや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wouldn’t? Whatever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "それより今からプレイするから楽屋に入って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ go back to the waiting room. It’s game time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4500,
          "startTime": 98.46666666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8643.33333333333,
          "startTime": 102.61
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 98.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 98.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "これを君に見せたかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is what I called you here to see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "見せたいものって、ライブのことじゃなかったのか？\n……音ゲー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not the live? Something else?\n…A rhythm game?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 108.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "僕、割とうまいんだ\n君に見てもらいたくてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m pretty good.\nI want to show you my skills.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なんでまた俺に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why me? Again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 113.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "君がゲームが趣味って言うから\nやってみたんじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you like games.\nThat’s why I even tried this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 117.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことか、まさかこの前の話を覚えていたとは\nそれにしても凄いな。ノーミスじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You actually went ahead with that.\nYou are good too. That was a perfect combo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 127.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_01_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、これは簡単な曲だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that’s one of the easier tracks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 129.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
